<lb ed="I" n="0057a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>比丘尼統慈慶墓誌銘</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb n="0058a" xml:id="I01.0022.0058a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0058a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0058a0101">魏故比丘<note n="0058001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB00112"/>＝尼【史】</note><note n="0058001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB00112"/>【佛拓】，尼【史】</note><app n="0058001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">尼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00112"/></rdg></app>統慈慶墓誌銘
<lb ed="I" n="0058a02"/><app type="star" corresp="#0058001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">尼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00112"/></rdg></app>俗姓王氏。字鍾兒。太原祁人。宕渠太守<note n="0058002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30472"/>＝虔【史】</note><note n="0058002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30472"/>【佛拓】，虔【史】</note><app n="0058002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虔</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30472"/></rdg></app>象之女也。稟氣<note n="0058003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30473"/>＝淑【史】</note><note n="0058003" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30473"/>【佛拓】，淑【史】</note><app n="0058003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淑</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30473"/></rdg></app>真。資
<lb ed="I" n="0058a03"/>神<note n="0058004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">烋＝休【史】</note><note n="0058004" resp="ihp" type="mod">烋【佛拓】，休【史】</note><app n="0058004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">休</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">烋</rdg></app>烈。理懷貞粹。志識寬遠。故溫敏之度發自齠華。而柔順之規邁
<lb ed="I" n="0058a04"/>于成德矣。年廿有四。適故豫州主薄行南頓太守恒農楊興宗。諧襟
<lb ed="I" n="0058a05"/>外族。執禮中饋。女功之事既<note n="0058005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB05895"/>＝緝【史】</note><note n="0058005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB05895"/>【佛拓】，緝【史】</note><app n="0058005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">緝</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB05895"/></rdg></app>。婦則之儀惟允。于時宗父坦之。出宰
<lb ed="I" n="0058a06"/>長社。率家從<note n="0058006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">軄＝職【史】</note><note n="0058006" resp="ihp" type="mod">軄【佛拓】，職【史】</note><app n="0058006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">職</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">軄</rdg></app>。爰寓豫州。值玄<note n="0058007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30475"/>＝瓠【史】</note><note n="0058007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30475"/>【佛拓】，瓠【史】</note><app n="0058007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瓠</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30475"/></rdg></app>鎮將汝南人常珍奇。據城反叛。以
<lb ed="I" n="0058a07"/>應外<note n="0058008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30476"/>＝寇【史】</note><note n="0058008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30476"/>【佛拓】，寇【史】</note><app n="0058008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">寇</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30476"/></rdg></app>。王師致討。掠沒奚官。遂為　恭宗景穆皇帝昭儀斛律氏。躬
<lb ed="I" n="0058a08"/><note n="0058009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30479"/>＝所【史】</note><note n="0058009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30479"/>【佛拓】，所【史】</note><app n="0058009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>養恤。共　文昭皇太后。有若同生。太和中固求出家。即居紫禁。<app type="star" corresp="#0058001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">尼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00112"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0058a09"/>之素行。爰協上下。秉是純心。彌貫終始。由是忍辱精進。德尚法流。仁
<lb ed="I" n="0058a10"/>和恭懿。行冠<note n="0058010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30477"/>＝椒【史】</note><note n="0058010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30477"/>【佛拓】，椒【史】</note><app n="0058010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">椒</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30477"/></rdg></app>列。侍護　先帝於弱立之辰。保衛　聖躬於載誕之
<lb ed="I" n="0058a11"/>日。雖劬勞密勿。未嘗懈其心。力衰年暮。莫敢<note n="0058011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">辤＝辭【史】</note><note n="0058011" resp="ihp" type="mod">辤【佛拓】，辭【史】</note><app n="0058011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辭</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">辤</rdg></app>其事。寔<note n="0058012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30478"/>＝亦【史】</note><note n="0058012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30478"/>【佛拓】，亦【史】</note><app n="0058012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亦</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30478"/></rdg></app>直道之<app type="star" corresp="#0058009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0058a12"/>依歸。慈誠之<app type="star" corresp="#0058009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30479"/></rdg></app>感結也。正光五年。<app type="star" corresp="#0058001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">尼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00112"/></rdg></app>之春秋八十有六。四月三日。忽
<lb ed="I" n="0058a13"/><note n="0058013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30480"/>＝遘【史】</note><note n="0058013" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30480"/>【佛拓】，遘【史】</note><app n="0058013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遘</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30480"/></rdg></app>時<note n="0058014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB11042"/>＝疹【史】</note><note n="0058014" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB11042"/>【佛拓】，疹【史】</note><app n="0058014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">疹</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB11042"/></rdg></app>。出居外寺。其月廿七日。　車駕躬臨省視。自旦達暮。親監藥
<lb ed="I" n="0058a14"/>劑。逮于大漸。餘氣將絕。猶<note n="0058015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30482"/>＝獻【史】</note><note n="0058015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30482"/>【佛拓】，獻【史】</note><app n="0058015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">獻</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30482"/></rdg></app>遺言。以贊政道。五月庚戌<note n="0058016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB09203"/>＝朔【史】</note><note n="0058016" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB09203"/>【佛拓】，朔【史】</note><app n="0058016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">朔</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB09203"/></rdg></app>七日丙辰。
<lb ed="I" n="0058a15"/>遷神于昭儀寺。　皇上傷悼。乃垂手　詔曰。<app type="star" corresp="#0058001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">尼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00112"/></rdg></app>　<note n="0058017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30483"/>＝歷【史】</note><note n="0058017" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30483"/>【佛拓】，歷【史】</note><app n="0058017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">歷</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30483"/></rdg></app>奉　五朝。崇重
<lb ed="I" n="0058a16"/>三帝。英名耆老。法門宿齒。并復東華兆建之日。朕躬誕育之初。每被
<lb ed="I" n="0058a17"/>恩<note n="0058018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">勑＝敕【史】</note><note n="0058018" resp="ihp" type="mod">勑【佛拓】，敕【史】</note><app n="0058018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">敕</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">勑</rdg></app>。委付侍守。昨以晡時。忽致殞逝。朕躬悲悼。用惕於懷。可給葬具。
<lb ed="I" n="0058a18"/>一依別<app type="star" corresp="#0058018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">敕</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">勑</rdg></app>。中給事中王紹。鑒<note n="0058019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30484"/>＝督【史】</note><note n="0058019" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30484"/>【佛拓】，督【史】</note><app n="0058019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">督</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30484"/></rdg></app>喪事。贈物一千五百段。又追贈比丘
<lb ed="I" n="0058a19"/><app type="star" corresp="#0058001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">尼</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00112"/></rdg></app>統。以十八日窆于洛陽北芒之山。乃命史臣作銘誌之。其詞曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0058a20"/>道性雖寂。淳氣未離。沖凝異揆。緇素同規。於昭<app type="star" corresp="#0058003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淑</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30473"/></rdg></app>敏。寔粹光儀。如雲
<lb ed="I" n="0058a21"/>出岫。若月臨池。契闊家艱。屯亶世故。信命安時。初睽末遇。孤影易彯。
<lb ed="I" n="0058a22"/>窮<note n="0058020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">昬＝昏【史】</note><note n="0058020" resp="ihp" type="mod">昬【佛拓】，昏【史】</note><app n="0058020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昏</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">昬</rdg></app>難曙。投迹四禪。邀誠六渡。直心既亮。練行斯敦。洞<note n="0058021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB00440"/>＝窺【史】</note><note n="0058021" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB00440"/>【佛拓】，窺【史】</note><app n="0058021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">窺</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00440"/></rdg></app>非想。玄照
<lb ed="I" n="0058a23"/>無言。注荷眷渥。茲負隆恩。空嗟落晷。徒勖告存。停壑不久。徂舟無舍。
<lb ed="I" n="0058a24"/>氣阻安般。神疲旦夜。延竚翠儀。淹留鑾駕。滅彩還機。夷襟從化。悲纏
<lb ed="I" n="0058a25"/>四眾。悼結兩宮。哀數加厚。窆禮增崇。泉幽閟景。隴首捿風。揚名述始。
<lb ed="I" n="0058a26"/>勒石追終。　征虜將軍中散大夫領中書舍人常景文　李寧民書</p></cb:div>
